comments: Gallinari (ATL) makes marginal contact to the body of Embiid (PHI) during his shooting motion that does not affect his play at the basket.

Young (ATL) and Maxey (PHI) engage in incidental body contact while trying to pursue the rebound. As Maxey gains control of the rebound he begins to fall to the ground but is able to make the pass to his teammate.
Young (ATL) makes foot to foot contact with Embiid (PHI) as he gathers and enters his upward shooting motion during the jump shot attempt.
Curry (PHI) makes clean contact with the ball before incidental body contact occurs with Young (ATL).
Collins (ATL) makes body contact with Harris (PHI) that forces him to go out of bounds before releasing the pass.
Huerter (ATL) commits a take foul on Maxey (PHI).
Young (ATL) commits a take foul on Maxey (PHI).
Thybulle (PHI) momentarily places an arm around the lower body of Young (ATL) in the backcourt, Young is able to move through the contact and his ability to receive the pass is not affected.
Thybulle (PHI) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Young (ATL) as he swipes and avoids making contact to the arm of Young during his play at the rim.
Collins (ATL) commits a take foul on Harris (PHI).
Williams (ATL) commits a take foul on Harris (PHI).
